description: Application for outline permission (all matters reserved) for mixed use development providing up to 863 residential units (equating to up to 112,800 sq m of residential floorspace) (Use Class C3) and up to 6900 sq m of commercial floorspace (Use Class A1-A3, B1, D1, D2) with open space and landscaping, ancillary facilities, related infrastructure and engineering works and vehicle access from Alma Street, Leyton Road and Henrietta Street.Zones 2-5.
